{{Han etym}}
In current form, {{Han compound|竹|目|廾|t1=bamboo}}.

The {{lang|zh|目}} portion may have originally represented [[w:Counting_rods|counting rods]] (or possibly an [[abacus]], although the character is believed to predate its invention). Such rods were typically made from bamboo.

